@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h2>Welcome to WebDJ!</h2>
    <p>
        WebDJ was my capstone project created for devCodeCamp, a software development and coding bootcamp based in Madison and Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
    </p><br />
        <ul>
            <li>
                Signing up for an account allows you to create 3 playlists of songs on spotify, with up to 20 songs per playlist.
            </li>
            <li>
                If you go to your profile page and sign up for 'premium' services, this is extended to 5 playlists with any number of songs.
            </li>
            <li>
                You can also follow other users, look at their playlists, and make your account private.
            </li>
            <li>
                If you have a premium account, you can even have a playlist of songs automatically generated for you!
            </li>
        </ul>
    <br />
    <p>
        Disclaimer: Most of the features on this website use the spotify API. If you do not have a spotify premium account, your access to the features of this website are severely limited.
    </p>
</div>
